<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. لَكِنَّهُمْ إِذْ آثَرُوا وَادِي تَخَيَّـ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>ـيَبَ أَصْبَحُوا أَعْدَاءَ هَذَا الشَّانِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَالْمُقْتَدِي بِالْوَحْيِ فِي أَعْمَالِهِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>يَلْقَى الأَذَى مِنْهُمْ وَكُلَّ هَوَانِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>لِعُدُولِهِ عَنْ أَخْذِهِ بِمَذَاهِبِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فِي الرَّأْيِ مَا قَامَتْ عَلَى بُرْهَانِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>جَعَلُوا مَذَاهِبَهُمْ مُسَيْطَرَةً عَلَى<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فَهْمِ الْحَدِيثِ وَمَنْزِلِ الْقُرْآنِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>ذَادُوا ذَوِي الأَلْبَابِ عَنْ فِقْهِ الْكِتا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>بِ وَفِقْهِ سُنَّةِ صَاحِبِ التِّبْيَانِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَغَدَتْ شَرِيعَتُنَا بِمُوجَبِ قَوْلِهِمْ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>مَنْسُوخَةٌ فِي هَذِهِ الأَزْمَانِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>حَجَبُوا مَحَاسِنَهَا بِتَأْوِيلاتِهِمْ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>فَغَدَتْ مِن الآرَاءِ فِي خُلْقَانِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَلَوْ أَنَّهَا بَرَزَتْ مُجَرَّدَةً لَهَا<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>مَ الأَذْكِيَاءُ بِحُسْنِهَا الْفَتَّانِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>لَكِنَّهُمْ قَامُوا حَوَائِلَ دُونَهَا<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>كَالأَوْصِيَاءِ لِقَاصِرِ الصِّبْيَانِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>مَا عِنْدَهُمْ عِنْدَ التَّنَاظُرِ حُجَّةٌ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>أَنَّى بِهَا لِمُقَلِّدِ حَيْرَانِ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>لا يَفْزَعُونَ إِلَى الدَّلِيلِ وَإِنَّمَا<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>